.TEMP 27

* Power Supplies
V3          cc 0 DC 20
V2          0 dd DC 20

* Input Voltage Source
* DC = 0V, AC = 1V, and 10uV peak, 10Hz sine wave for transient analysis (in-band)
Vin          in 0 DC 0 AC 1 SIN(0 10u 10)

* Circuit Netlist
C6          0 8 163N 
C5          9 out 163N 
C4          11 6 33N 
C3          5 12 33N 
C2          13 4 33N 
C1          3 14 33N 
R10         6 8 750 
R9          8 0 10K 
